{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2546","id":3752616341,"node_id":"PR_kwDOEHbxG87frGGV","html_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2546","diff_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2546.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doldecomp/melee/pull/2546.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2546","number":2546,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"resplit it_2725.c","user":{"login":"lukechampine","id":3344749,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMzNDQ3NDk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3344749?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine","html_url":"https://github.com/lukechampine","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/lukechampine/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"bit of a doozy here, sorry.\r\n\r\nAs I close in on matching all of `it/`, it's becoming necessary to revisit some of the splits. I had Claude and Codex iteratively split it_2725 into a bunch of TUs based on the presence of repeated floats/strings. This was what they came up with:\r\n\r\n`it_2725`: Purpose still unclear. Codex suggested calling it `itcommon`.\r\n`ithitbox`:  Functions are clustered around item hitbox setup, scaling, state toggles, and hitbox-derived collision queries.\r\n`itmaplib`: Item map collision behavior: ECB setup, floor/wall/ceiling contact handling, normals, bounce, slide, and map-relative rotation. Filename found in `__assert(\"itmaplib.c\", ...)`\r\n`itmaterial`: Code that directly manipulates item HSD_MObj, HSD_TExp, render mode, and GXColor material state. Filename found in `struct it_MObjInfo it_803F1F90` object.\r\n`iteffect`: Item effect helpers, including effect archive setup and spawning randomized sync effects.\r\n`itanimlist`: Item animation-command handlers taking `CommandInfo*` and dispatching animation-list side effects. Filename found in `__assert(\"itanimlist.c\", ...)`\r\n`it_279C`: Aggregates Pokémon, character-specific, monster, and stage-item tables plus shared helpers. Codex suggested `itspecial`, but with low confidence.\r\n`itzako`: Zako/enemy-style items, including grzakogenerator use. Filename inferred from a `\"can t init zako pos\\n\"` string.\r\n\r\nAll of these are matching and linked except `itmaplib`.\r\n\r\nRemaining item TUs: 20\r\nRemaining item functions: 84","created_at":"2026-05-27T04:14:10Z","updated_at":"2026-05-27T14:35:01Z","closed_at":"2026-05-27T14:33:57Z","merged_at":"2026-05-27T14:33:57Z","merge_commit_sha":"0a47255a9650693cb98a3faee6196073786c8aa8","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2546/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2546/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2546/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/f9d589a0107c657a44abc895080b7ad128d03621","head":{"label":"lukechampine:split-2725","ref":"split-2725","sha":"f9d589a0107c657a44abc895080b7ad128d03621","user":{"login":"lukechampine","id":3344749,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMzNDQ3NDk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3344749?v=4